Surya Kriya - Fire up the Sun within
 

Surya Kriya is to activate the internal sun, but you stimulate it by using the external sun.

- Sadhguru

Surya Kriya, the forefather to Surya Namaskar (Sun Salutation) is a powerful process of activating the sun within you. It balances a person’s energies, leading to stability of the body and stillness of the mind. This strong foundation becomes the basis to explore higher dimensions of life.
  • Develops mental clarity and focus
  • Remedies weak constitutions
  • Balances hormonal levels in the body
  • Prepares one for deeper states of meditation

Date & Time:
7-8 April 2017, 8 am - 11 am

Angamardana - The Ultimate Yogic Workout
 

Angamardana is a system rooted in yoga, that offers to everyone the opportunity to invigorate the body and to reach peak physical and mental health.

"Angamardana" means, gaining complete mastery over the limbs, organs and other parts of the body. True to its name, this practice revitalizes the body on all levels including the muscles, blood circulation, skeletal structure, nervous system, and the basic energy system.

  • Strengthens the spine, skeletal and muscular system
  • Builds physical strength, fitness and tenacity
  • Takes years off the body, bringing a sense of lightness and freedom
  • Prepares the body for Hatha Yoga
